terjadi padamu tiba-tiba?

00:04:11.840 --> 00:04:12.960
Apa?

00:04:27.800 --> 00:04:29.880
Dokter, saline...
- Anda telah memberi saya saline.

00:04:31.600 --> 00:04:33.120
